>\n同埋用威權令淺藍唔敢有行動"},{"pid":"e33b4ce286ded8315d6726a2601df2adb9f3ada4","tid":1614505,"uid":299085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17a5671cae3b994c3aeeae5d12d95c2809f20dc","tid":1614505,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:18:05.000Z","msg":"睇 論持久戰<br />\n毛主席講哂點打<br />\n當popo 係日軍就ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"佢都冇打日軍。<br />\n樓主用國民黨做比喻係正解。"}]}